{"tid":1639761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【資料庫】Lord賓把握力更勝福仔","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:02:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03512f43e34d1585572d8b7d30edc0de3be8871f","tid":1639761,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】英國傳媒《太陽報》指出，曼聯前鋒華舒福的把握力比前阿仙奴名將賓特拿更差。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯前鋒華舒福（Marcus Rashford）出道時驚為天人，只是今季擔起9號位重任，表現令人失望。英國傳媒《太陽報》作統計，發現華舒福出道至今的表現，居然比前阿仙奴前鋒賓特拿更差。<br />\n<br />\n華舒福於2016年出道至今共上陣180場比賽共攻入48球，場均入球只得0.266球，每隔3.75場比賽才有1球進賬。賓特拿效率更高，上陣了171場比賽共入了47球，場均入球有0.275球，每隔3.63場比賽便利有1球進賬。<br />\n<br />\n今季華舒福踢得艱苦，阿仙奴名宿基昂便說：「當我看到曼聯不斷放長傳給華舒福時，我便對此感到傷心。我認為他開始對周圍的事物感到絕望，他沒有在球場上走動。他是個很好的球員，但我不知道他在等甚麼。」"},{"pid":"66c6145ede985c1daf3fd8747d42f227db8a7088","tid":1639761,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.bleacherreport.net/temp_images/2013/12/04/iwrBurj9qZyt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.bleacherreport.net%2Ftemp_images%2F2013%2F12%2F04%2FiwrBurj9qZyt.gif&h=8ccca2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nN賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec43095542dfd7508b06c6f1f6de02a8d93313f","tid":1639761,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/SneakyIncredibleAdouri-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FSneakyIncredibleAdouri-max-1mb.gif&h=655358b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/TidyLimpingImperatorangel-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FTidyLimpingImperatorangel-max-1mb.gif&h=00323539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLord賓防守力更勝VVD"},{"pid":"fe456f5360ba92885c58